description:
In this very special Everything Iconic POP Dive, we take the podcast on the road to explore two iconic #RHOC locations-- the ropes course and the not-very-quiet restaurant, The Quiet Woman ("This isn't my plate...!"). Along the way we drink more than planned and chat with #RHOC cast member Emily Simpson, Kate Casey (Reality Life with Kate Casey), Troy Turner (Taste of Reality with Troy Turner), Amanda Hasaka, Adam Salandra, and more!


*To support this podcast & get bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
